{"tid":932554,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聯邦檢察官最快下周將起訴一些與中國國安部門有關連的駭客","createTime":"2018-12-07T22:52:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-09T16:00:44.000Z","uid":147314,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"fe1ae029c55a9fba1e0c8bfa5799964e209d6fc1","tid":932554,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T22:52:08.000Z","msg":"<strong>傳美國將檢控中國駭客活動</strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">今日 05:36</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2018/12/08/2010877_7268feb61953532291d1d41d5c42c787.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2018%2F12%2F08%2F2010877_7268feb61953532291d1d41d5c42c787.jpg&h=338b9a98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《華爾街日報》引述消息人士稱，美國檢察官最快下周將起訴一些與中國國安部門有關連的駭客，涉嫌偷取美國公司的商業機密。<br />\n<br />\n披露消息的美國情報機關主管稱，該項中國駭客的行動代號為Cloudhopper，將是有紀錄以來最昂貴與成功的駭客入侵個案之一。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，被駭客偷取機密的美國企業很廣泛，因為Cloudhopper針對偷入大型代第三方保管數據的科技企業。<br />\n<br />\n美國司法部與國安部門拒評上述消息。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2010877/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2010877%2F&d=YgRU0upirhQ4ZjU58MBUaP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=38f85b95\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2010877/</a>"},{"pid":"5a7cf497a1132017fee63de2a20559322dada5f5","tid":932554,"uid":147314,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T22:53:38.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">U.S. Readies Charges Against Chinese Hackers</span></strong><br />\nGovernment-linked hackers allegedly engaged in a multiyear scheme to break into U.S. technology service providers<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wsj.com/articles/u-s-readies-charges-against-chinese-hackers-1544206196\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fu-s-readies-charges-against-chinese-hackers-1544206196&d=YgRU0up